Benjamin B. Morris, Appellee, v. Wacker Hotel Company et al., Appellants.Gen. No. 42,722.

Matchett, J., dissents.

Heard in the first division, first district, this court at the June term, 1943;opinion filed February 18, 1944;supplemental opinion filed and rehearing denied March 2, 1944.Brown, Fox & Blumberg, for appellants; Charles LeRoy Brown and Jacob Logan Fox, of counsel; David I. Spark, for appellee.

Opinion by

Presiding Justice O’Connor.

Not to be published in. full.
